canonicalsolution

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • canonicalsolution.Command

  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Processes each command in the MeeshQuest program. Takes in an XML command node, processes the node, and outputs the results.
    Version:
    2.0, 23 Jan 2007
    Author:
    Ben Zoller

      • processCommands

        public void processCommands(org.w3c.dom.Element node)

        Parameters:
        node - commands node to be processed

      • processCreateCity

        public void processCreateCity(org.w3c.dom.Element node)
        Processes a createCity command. Creates a city in the dictionary (Note: does not map the city). An error occurs if a city with that name or location is already in the dictionary.
        Parameters:
        node - createCity node to be processed

      • processDeleteCity

        public void processDeleteCity(org.w3c.dom.Element node)
        Processes a deleteCity command. Deletes a city from the dictionary. An error occurs if the city does not exist or is currently mapped.
        Parameters:
        node - deleteCity node being processed
